title: Haggard Wulf - Howlin' B-Sides And Rarities [FLAC]
description:
Haggard Wulf are a 2-piece band from Morgantown, WV, who bring together
a mixture of blues, rockabilly and punk rock. Their sound and style is
diverse, bringing a very full sound to the table. They have a very strong DIY
ethic, much like the punk bands of the late 70s and early 80s. Check them out here:



This 11 track album was released by Wild Raft Records on June 10, 2013.

Tracklist:

1. Bath Salt Blues (3:45)	
2. The Tall Man (3:55)
3. Night Of The Vampire (3:40)	
4. Bad Side Of Town [Acoustic] (3:07)	
5. Been Down So Long [Acoustic] (3:58)	
6. Never Bet The Devil Your Head [Alt. Version] (5:21)	
7. Death Parade [Alt. Version] (3:43)
8. The Floorboards [Alt. Version] (2:31)
9. I'm On The Other Side [Live at Howlers] (4:19)
10. There's A Ghost In Your House [Live at Howlers] (3:35)
11. X = Haggard [Live at Raiders] (2:23)
